CHANGES IN VERSION 0.2-0 (2013-11-7)

    o Initialized the package with the following functions:
      (lower and upper incomplete) Gamma function, 
      (incomplete) Beta function, Psi function, and
      Gauss' Hypergeometric function 2F1
    o NEWS added and submitted to CRAN.

CHANGES IN VERSION 0.1-0 (2013-11-3)

    o Setup package `specfun' and submitted to R-Forge
